            <h2 class="page__title">The Neurobiology of Grace Under Pressure</h2>

      
              <div class="blog-subtitle">
          8 habits that stimulate your vagus nerve and keep you calm, cool, and collected.        </div>
        <div class="fb-like-button">
          <div id="fb-root"></div><script src="https://cdn.psychologytoday.com/sites/all/modules/custom/pt_facebook/js/pt_facebook.like.js"></script><div class="fb-like" data-href="https://www.psychologytoday.com/blog/the-athletes-way/201302/the-neurobiology-grace-under-pressure" data-layout="button_count" data-action="like" data-show-faces="false" data-share="false"></div>        </div>
        <div class="blog__author-description subtext">
          Posted Feb 02, 2013        </div>
