    <h3 class="comment__title"><a href="/comment/909347#comment-909347" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">Coherent Breathing</a></h3>
  
  <div class="submitted subtext">
    Submitted by wilfried on March 20, 2017 - 4:07am  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
        <div class="field__item"><p>Another effective tool to improve the vagal tone and the vagal brake according to Steven Porges is Coherent Breathing, breathing in a rhythm that balances the nervous system and strengthens the parasympathicus (measurable via heart rate variability).<br />
Read<br />
Wilfried Ehrmann: Coherent Breathing (2017) or Stephen Elliott: The New Science of Breath (2005)</p>
