    <h3 class="comment__title"><a href="/comment/825890#comment-825890" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">Fascinating and true...</a></h3>
  
  <div class="submitted subtext">
    Submitted by Shubha on March 12, 2016 - 2:28pm  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden">
        <div class="field__item"><p>This is well written and well explained. I have often felt the stress and experienced the positive effects of destressing through diaphragmatic breathing. Similarly, I have known the contagious nature of anxiety from anxious people around me. Especially when I am waiting for important meetings or interviews. I adopted the same means of keeping my distance during that time and refocusing on the positives. Although, I acknowledge that more scientific evidence is needed appease the sceptics.</p>
